          ],
          "text": "With that, I got the updateNet() to about 50 ms and the verifyNets() nearly instantanously as well. However, paintEvent() still takes a long time. Why?",
          "uuid": "69bc4189"
        }
      ]
    },
    { "typ": "textblock",
      "cre": "2026-06-07T16:51:33.981",
      "mod": "2026-06-07T16:52:00.594",
      "h": 73.498,
      "ind": 1,
      "sheet": 0,
      "split": [ ],
      "uuid": "bb22c962",
      "y0": 145.498,
      "cc": [
        { "typ": "text",
          "cre": "2026-06-07T16:51:33.981",
          "mod": "2026-06-07T16:52:00.594",
          "lines": [
            0,
            64,
            130
          ],
          "text": "I  made it a lot better by replacing NodeID with a std::vector. I also tried std::list and std::deque, but vector was faster than either.",
          "uuid": "b80aeffa"
        }
      ]
    },
    { "typ": "textblock",
      "cre": "2026-06-07T16:52:05.617",
      "mod": "2026-06-07T16:52:42.088",
      "h": 50.332,
      "ind": 1,
